    {
      "id": "line-002",
      "start": 7.04,
      "end": 11.86,
      "text": "For more information or to volunteer, please visit LibraVox.org.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 12.74,
      "end": 14.1,
      "text": "Recorded by Kim Braun.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 15.78,
      "end": 18.58,
      "text": "Asop's fables, the escaped Jackdaw.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 20.16,
      "end": 25.62,
      "text": "A man caught a Jackdaw and tied a piece of string to one of its legs, and then gave it",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 25.62,
      "end": 26.96,
      "text": "to his children for a pet.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 27.54,
      "end": 30.94,
      "text": "But the Jackdaw didn't at all like having to live with people.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 31.56,
      "end": 37.12,
      "text": "So, after a while, when he seemed to have become fairly tame and they didn't watch him so closely,",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 37.66,
      "end": 39.96,
      "text": "he slipped away and flew back to his old haunts.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 41.32,
      "end": 46.72,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the string was still on his leg, and before long it got entangled in the branches",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 46.72,
      "end": 50.72,
      "text": "of a tree, and the Jackdaw couldn't get free, try as he would.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 50.72,
      "end": 59.08,
      "text": "He saw it was all up with him and cried in despair, alas and gaining my freedom, I have lost my life.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-013",
      "start": 60.2,
      "end": 62.36,
      "text": "End of the escaped Jackdaw.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
